modName: FUN HOUSE for AP and Enhanced Hotpools
summary: I made a bedroom for AP users. It\'s near hotpools and has a passage to Winking Skeever. Bed is player owned, so you can use AP options on bed. Your followers can get in too.
descriptionHtml:
I made a bedroom for AP users. It\'s near hotpools and has a passage to Winking Skeever. Bed is player owned, so you can use AP options on bed. Your followers can get in too.
